data.description: Actibe with contract, back up offers only. Your search ends here with this lovely Mediterranean style 3/2/2 with pool in Seven Hills. Screened front porch allows breezy cross ventilation. Enter through double entry doors into tiled foyer with a large coat closet. Newer, gleaming tile floors throughout most of the home. Popular open great room plan with beamed cathedral ceiling with fan and triple pocket sliders to Florida room. Formal dining room with nice windows. Kitchen features beautiful granite counters, a breakfast bar, tile back splash and eat in nook. Master suite has double doors, 2 walk in closets, a jetted soaking tub to relax in, separate shower, a separate commode with bidet attachment. Guest bedrooms in this split plan home have Berber carpet and ceiling fans, one bedroom is not pictured yet.  Inside laundry room has sink, stacking washer and dryer can stay.  Florida room has carpet and wall A/C unit which can add 428' of living space to this already good sized home. The inviting solar heated 14 x 28 pool is possibly the best part of this home, with pavered floor, screens replaced in '21, and pop up cleaning heads. Garage door and A/C were replaced in 2014, roof in '09. Located in popular Seven Hills community with low annual HOA fees of just $240 a year. The YMCA is within a half mile of this home, with a variety of fitness classes and equipment. Very close to many stores, medical facilities and restaurants. An easy commute to the Suncoast Parkway entrance to get to the Tampa airport in 40 minutes, or enjoy the museums and activities in the city. Weeki Wachee Springs is a short drive west, as are Roger's Park and Pine Island for some of Florida's spectacular sunsets. Call today to see this gem!
